- whether_is_abnormal_metric(container.cpu.usage) for the affected containers (cartservice-1, recommendationservice-2, productcatalogservice-0, frontend-* ) around the timestamps;
- whether_is_abnormal_metric(node.cpu.usage) for their nodes;
- whether_is_abnormal_metric(container.network.tcp.retransmits) and packet-drop counters for those containers/nodes;
- collect_trace on a slow trace and inspect span breakdown (server processing vs network/wait times).
